texts.text: Each of the jails have a Vindicator spawn in front of the doors.
The two cobblestone stairs are upside down and face each other.
The Medium Jail is also known as the Redstone Jail.
All of the cobblestone stairs are upside down.

The oak wood stairs on Layer 1 past row 10 are upside down.
The cobblestone stairs on Layer 4 are upside down and face inside.
